[node name="HelpContent" type="Label" parent="HelpPage"]
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 40.0
offset_top = 70.0
offset_right = 900.0
offset_bottom = 620.0
theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 14
text = "=== Game Rules ===
Goal: Play all cards first
Play must be stronger than table cards (smaller atomic sum = stronger)
Cannot play? Pass (draw 1 card)

=== Card Types ===
【Element】1 card or 2 diatomic (H₂/N₂/O₂/F₂/Cl₂)
【Compound】Multi-element valence match, exact ratio
  Metal as cation, non-metal as anion
【Clan Bomb】Same group >=2 different elements
  3-card bomb > 2-card bomb

=== Play Rules ===
Table has element → play stronger element/clan bomb
Table has compound → play stronger compound/clan bomb
Clan bomb → clockwise intercept → winner free play
Overflow compound (>player count) → immune!"

